dc_description_s: This polygon data layer represents zoning for St. Croix County, Wisconsin in 2015. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, St_Croix_Zoning_2015.gdb. [The zoning classification defined at the parcel level, but typically managed in larger units.]
uw_supplemental_s: This metadata was updated to reflect that the data is no longer restricted and has been opened for public use. Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.
